All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
Camp
The Camp class represents an event or program organized by a school or a specific faculty.
CampList
The CampList class represents a list of camps, providing methods for creating, editing, and managing camp details.
CampManager
The CampManager class provides methods for managing camps, including creating new camps, editing existing camps, deleting camps, and toggling camp visibility.
CampRegistration
The CampRegistration class provides methods for students to register for camps, specifying their roles as either camp attendees or camp committee members.
CampRegistrationValidation
The CampRegistrationValidation class provides methods for validating various conditions related to camp registration, such as checking whether a student is eligible to register for a camp, verifying registration status, detecting date clashes, and evaluating slot availability.
CampWithdrawal
The CampWithdrawal class provides functionality for withdrawing a Student from a Camp.
CCMCampReportService
The CCMCampReportService class provides functionality to generate a report for a Camp Committee Member (CCM).
CCMCampViewService
The CCMCampViewService class provides a service for viewing camp details specifically designed for Camp Committee Members (CCM).
CCMMenu
The CCMMenu class provides functionalities and features available exclusively to Camp Committee Members (CCMs).
CCMSuggestionManager
The CCMSuggestionManager class extends FeedbackManager and provides functionality specific to handling suggestions made by Camp Committee Members (CCM).
Enquiry
Represents an Enquiry made by a student regarding a camp, along with its status and responses.
EnquiryList
Represents a list of enquiries with operations to manage enquiry-related functionalities.
EnquiryReportService
The EnquiryReportGenerationService class provides functionality to generate an Excel report for the enquiries related to a specific camp.
FeedbackList<T>
The FeedbackList interface outlines the common operations for managing feedback in a generic list.
FeedbackManager
The FeedbackManager abstract class provides a common interface for managing feedback.
Filter
The Filter class provides filtering options for camps and attendees.
MainApplication
Main Application class responsible for managing the CAMs (Camps Application and Management System).
ObjectFinder
The ObjectFinder class provides methods for finding objects such as Enquiry, Suggestion, Student, and Camp within their respective lists.
PerformanceReportService
The PerformanceReportService class provides functionalities to generate performance reports for selected camps and their committee members.
Staff
Represents a Staff member, extending the functionality of a User in the system.
StaffAndCCMEnquiryManager
The StaffAndCCMEnquiryManager class provides methods for both staff members and Camp Committee Members (CCMs) to manage and respond to enquiries related to camps.
StaffCampReportService
The StaffCampReportService class provides functionality to generate reports for camps associated with a staff member.
StaffCampViewService
The StaffCampViewService class provides methods for staff members to view details of camps, including a list of all camps, camps created by the staff, and details of a specific camp.
StaffList
Represents a list of staff members with user management operations.
StaffMenu
The StaffMenu class represents the menu and functionality available to staff members within the application.
StaffSuggestionManager
The StaffSuggestionManager class manages the processing of suggestions by staff members.
Student
Represents a Student, extending the functionality of a User in the system.
StudentCampViewService
The StudentCampViewService class provides methods for viewing available camps and registered camps for a student.
StudentEnquiryManager
The StudentEnquiryManager class manages student enquiries for camps, allowing students to submit, delete, edit, and view their enquiries.
StudentList
Represents a list of students with user management operations.
StudentMenu
The StudentMenu class represents the menu options available for a student in the system.
Suggestion
Represents a suggestion made by a camp committee member for a camp, including its status and approval details.
SuggestionList
Represents a list of suggestions with operations to manage suggestion-related functionalities.
User
Represents a user in the system
UserList
Represents an interface for managing user-related operations within a user list.
